highlights.text: Tobias Sten has the most spots on Top Songs Norway. “Ingen her e deg” is the highest at #4.
“Piano Man” by Billy Joel is the highest new entry on Top Songs Norway at #189.

“Her kommer Bjørnis” by Brannbamsen Bjørnis is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Norway, up 44 spots at #132.
